		<p>Good for you!  I applaud your decision.  </p>
<p>I had already donated to help make the film and bought the two different DVDs (which came with the free film as a bonus!)  </p>
<p>Time to buy me some merchandise.  I think I need some cool t shirts for pottery class!</p>
<p>- Michael</p>
		</div>
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li class="pingback odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-40129">
		<div id="div-comment-40129" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<span class="authorname"><a href='http://freedomforip.org/2010/04/26/netflix-loses-sita-over-bad-drm-choice/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Netflix Loses Sita Over Bad DRM Choice | Freedom for IP</a></span>
		</div>
				<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/04/23/turning-down-netflix/comment-page-1/#comment-40129">
		April 26, 2010 at 11:56 am</a>
        		 
		</div>
		<p>[...] Netflix refuses to stream Sita Sings the Blues without DRM. The artist, Nina paley, wants her movie distributed DRM-free! Nina was even willing to compromise by using DRM but inserting a message before the movie pointing to where people can get it for free without DRM. Netflix would not budge on the issue. this resulted in Nina turning down a 5k contract and netflix losing out on a great movie we can all see elsewhere for free. I’ve been the “change I want to see” in regards to copyright monopolies. People told me I’d lose everything by copylefting Sita, including all hope of professional distribution. But in fact, some professional distributors became willing to distribute Sita without claiming monopolies over it, and we’re all fine. [...]</p>
		</div>
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li class="pingback even thread-even depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-40131">
		<div id="div-comment-40131" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<span class="authorname"><a href='http://www.animaxionstudioz.com/?p=874' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Nina Paley: uma animadora com princípios! | animaXion studioz</a></span>
		</div>
